Dr. Christensen,<br><br>
I have visited The Wall twice, alone. It brings back feelings, memories, and flashbacks of those events now more than 25 years ago. I cannot touch the wall, for I, and many others, are really a part of it in our minds.<br><br>
I appreciate and thank you for your sharing your experience at The Wall. It validates and honors all who served, and those who served and did not return.<br><br>
Arthur Varanelli, RVN 69-70<br>
 
